    "description": "<div>Hey <bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiKWdpZDovL2JjMy9QZXJzb24vNDczMzY1MjE_ZXhwaXJlc19pbgY7AFRJIghwdXIGOwBUSSIPYXR0YWNoYWJsZQY7AFQ=--82970c142b3c5ce53fa08908c4a9e56603a70a4a\" content-type=\"application/vnd.basecamp.mention\"><figure>\n  <img data-avatar-for-person-id=\"47336521\" alt=\"Ethan Vandenberg\" title=\"Ethan Vandenberg, Account Manager at Clixsy\" class=\"avatar\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://bc3-production-assets-cdn.basecamp-static.com/4226914/people/BAhpBElM0gI=--35650f63c96baab38ba9231e4ef89b3fd94ce1f7/avatar\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\">\n  <figcaption>\n    Ethan\n  </figcaption>\n</figure></bc-attachment>,<br><br>Do you have any information on whether the GBP numbers are all unique local numbers or GBP tracking numbers, by chance? I wanted to check in with you before we go to the client in case this info is already housed somewhere that I am not privy to.<br><br>None of the numbers appear on the site, as there are no numbers alongside the address in the footer. <br>Besides one \"contact us\" number (405-725-1534).<br><br><br>Here are the numbers on each GBP:<br><br><strong>MIDWEST CITY<br></strong>(405) 342-8546<br><br><strong>EDMOND</strong><br>(405) 591-3022<br><br><strong>NORMAN</strong><br>(405) 261-1664<br><br><strong>NICHOLS HILLS<br></strong>(405) 267-4996<br><br><strong>YUKON</strong><br>(405) 554-0053<br><br><bc-attachment sgid=\"BAh7BkkiC19yYWlscwY6BkVUewdJIglkYXRhBjsAVEkiLmdpZDovL2JjMy9BdHRhY2htZW50Lzc3MzYyNDMxNj9leHBpcmVzX2luBjsAVEkiCHB1cgY7AFRJIg9hdHRhY2hhYmxlBjsAVA==--a4b086cafc400d76cff8f49e4be581259d05efaa\" content-type=\"image/png\" url=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/44e128a0-a876-11f0-b862-0242ac120005/previews/full\" href=\"https://storage.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/44e128a0-a876-11f0-b862-0242ac120005/download/image.png\" filename=\"image.png\" filesize=\"218505\" width=\"1705\" height=\"887\" previewable=\"true\" presentation=\"gallery\"><figure>\n    <img srcset=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/44e128a0-a876-11f0-b862-0242ac120005/previews/full?dppx=2 2x, https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/44e128a0-a876-11f0-b862-0242ac120005/previews/full?dppx=1 1x, https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/44e128a0-a876-11f0-b862-0242ac120005/previews/full?dppx=3 3x, https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/44e128a0-a876-11f0-b862-0242ac120005/previews/full?dppx=4 4x\" src=\"https://preview.3.basecamp.com/4226914/blobs/44e128a0-a876-11f0-b862-0242ac120005/previews/full\">\n  <figcaption>\n    image.png\n  </figcaption>\n</figure></bc-attachment>\n</div>",
