    "comments_count": 3,
    "assignees": "Naas Van Zyl",
    "app_url": "https://3.basecamp.com/4226914/buckets/43339319/todos/9434424993",
    "description": "<div>\n<strong><br></strong><br>\n</div><div>\n<strong><br>Summary:</strong><br> We optimized the <em>Gas Line Repair</em> service page on <strong>callthechamps.com</strong> for stronger <strong>local and semantic SEO performance</strong>.<br> The update aligns the page with high-intent keywords — <em>gas line repair</em>, <em>gas line replacement</em>, <em>gas leak repair</em>, and <em>Edmond OK</em> — to improve relevance, authority, and search visibility.<br><br>\n</div><div>\n<strong><br>What we did:<br></strong><br>\n</div><ul>\n<li>\n<br>Rewrote on-page copy for clarity and entity alignment (repair + replacement + installation).<br><br>\n</li>\n<li>\n<br>Added optimized <strong>title tag</strong> and <strong>meta description</strong> for local CTR.<br><br>\n</li>\n<li>\n<br>Built and installed a <strong>comprehensive schema</strong> including:<br><br><ul>\n<li>\n<br>PlumbingService (LocalBusiness)<br><br>\n</li>\n<li>\n<br>Multiple Service nodes (repair, replacement, installation, leak detection)<br><br>\n</li>\n<li>\n<br>FAQPage for enhanced SERP rich results<br><br>\n</li>\n<li>\n<br>BreadcrumbList and WebPage structure for better crawlability.<br><br>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<br>Ensured full compliance with semantic SEO and structured-data best practices.<br><br>\n</li>\n</ul><div>\n<strong><br>Goal:</strong><br> Increase topical authority and click-through rates for gas-related plumbing services in Edmond and the Oklahoma City area.</div>",
    "visible_to_clients": false
  },
